==========================================================
AEGISNET PHASE 2
VISION TRIAGE ENGINE (THE ANALYST)
==========================================================

GOAL:
-----
Phase 2 identifies WHICH malware family a suspicious file
belongs to using Artificial Intelligence and Computer Vision.


WHY PHASE 2 EXISTS:
-------------------

Phase 1 can tell us:

    "Something malicious is happening."

But Phase 1 cannot tell us:

    "Which malware is causing it?"

Phase 2 answers that question.


